title: Kim Kardashian Is Furious That Duchess Kate Middleton Refuses to Meet Her
text: Kim Kardashian and Kanye West consider themselves “American Royalty,” so it only makes sense for them to want, if not actually expect, to be allowed access to actual royalty. Duchess Kate Middleton insists this won’t happen while she has a say, driving Kim mad with frustration. Kim and the Duchess have been compared a lot in recent years: both are very popular, both got married at about the same time and had their first child months apart. Both get a lot of media attention ... »
